nodes.text: Coruscant red wine vinaigrette was a salad dressing originating on Coruscant. The dressing was made from red wine and served over fresh greens. Coruscant red wine vinaigrette was served with fresh greens from Ithor aboard the luxury repulsortrain Gem of Alderaan and with fresh Barnaban greens at the annual Vor-cal Feast held aboard the House Melantha Orbital Hunting Lodge over the planet Vycinyth.
